{"tid":503847,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「中學雞」概率題求解","createTime":"2017-12-19T09:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T12:15:59.000Z","uid":137088,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"236861dc770bb7c2838c2b2b4d6abec4e264e677","tid":503847,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:45:40.000Z","msg":"一箱內有A，B，C，D，E 5個波<br />\n<br />\n5%抽到ABCD其中一個（隨機）<br />\n95%抽到E<br />\n<br />\n每次抽完把波放回箱內<br />\n問：<br />\nA抽齊ABCD(每樣最少1個）的平均次數是多少？<br />\nB抽到ABCD其中三個(每樣最少1個）的平均次數是多少？<br />\nC抽到ABCD其中二個(每樣最少1個）的平均次數是多少？<br />\nD抽到ABCD其中一個(每樣最少1個）的平均次數是多少？"},{"pid":"6ac17011d8c05e4e29fbffc91159b012ede8e871","tid":503847,"uid":2419,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:47:34.000Z","msg":"功課自己做啦"},{"pid":"5e7d72ef84d737983df0aef1351a431b2b14f9fd","tid":503847,"uid":103322,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"ABCD係波定係人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18a9a907773f0b53d207f7f07647781b723d6ec","tid":503847,"uid":67903,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"教你都得<br />\n但我用開英文做數<br />\n翻譯做英文先ok?"},{"pid":"0f115a5663e035da598dce88b64d84f2cce6032a","tid":503847,"uid":73737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"問阿Sir喇"},{"pid":"88d352a703f01facc6b5021ab46309c669ab7187","tid":503847,"uid":139228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"ABCD 唔係均等<br />\n咁要點計？"},{"pid":"6a4bfb86db542928e74c20c426cb46f8c318ab6a","tid":503847,"uid":7043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:06:17.000Z","msg":"望期值 <br />\n自己計啦"},{"pid":"bb77042d633ca094e810958a039b776fa701ad31","tid":503847,"uid":99828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"屌當撚咗呢度係上網問功課啊？"},{"pid":"fab767949cac5f66432488c74c664f60765dd438","tid":503847,"uid":89956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:49:47.000Z","msg":"當你係擁有ABCD其中N個既時候<br />\n需要再抽達至擁有其中兩個既期望次數係X(N)<br />\n咁X(2)=0，因為如果你有兩個你就唔需要繼續抽<br />\nX(1)=0.05*0.75*X(2)+(1-0.05*0.75)*X(1)+1<br />\n因為當你擁有其中一個既時候，再抽一次會有0.05*0.75咁多機會變成擁有兩個<br />\n得出X(1)=80/3<br />\n同樣X(0)=0.05*X(1)+0.95*X(0)+1<br />\n得出X(0)=140/3"},{"pid":"eeb35facbcaec8e36b8171cefb58c090bd3505d6","tid":503847,"uid":137088,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你係擁有ABCD其中N個既時候<br />\n需要再抽達至擁有其中兩個既期望次數係X(N)<br />\n咁X(2)=0，因為如果你有兩個你就唔需要繼續抽<br />\nX(1)=0.05*0.75*X(2)+(1-0.05*0.75)*X(1)+1<br />\n因為當你擁有其中一個既時候，再抽一次會有0.05*0.75咁多機會變成擁有兩個<br />\n得出X(1)=80/3<br />\n同樣X(0)=0.05*X(1)+0.95*X(0)+1<br />\n得出X(0)=140/3</blockquote><br />\n每一句都睇得明明地<br />\n加埋一齊就唔睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120e5a541fb8db62018d7bbd3458ae7534b1d4fd","tid":503847,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c134a822f169aa57d4e5a725460cd8b740cbd0","tid":503847,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:37:48.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c7773cd139c1f8579a26275cc4a6d98325577306","tid":503847,"uid":155029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:15:59.000Z","msg":"expected frequency = 1/expected value<br />\n大部分學校無教的<br />\n<br />\n甘你計先計左佢地expected value 先啦<br />\n<br />\nExample: <br />\n<br />\na part<br />\nexpected value= 4P4x(5%)^4<br />\n<br />\nexpected frequency = 1/{4P4x(5%)^4}"}]}